<h2 id="문제-하노이-탑-이동-순서">문제: <a href="https://www.acmicpc.net/problem/11729">하노이 탑 이동 순서</a></h2>

<div class="language-java highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="c1">// N-1 개의 원판을 목적지가 아닌 곳으로 옮긴다.</span>
<span class="n">move</span><span class="o">(</span><span class="no">N</span> <span class="o">-</span> <span class="mi">1</span><span class="o">,</span> <span class="n">start</span><span class="o">,</span> <span class="n">sub</span><span class="o">,</span> <span class="n">end</span><span class="o">);</span>
<span class="c1">// 제일 큰 원판을 목표 타워로 옮긴다.</span>
<span class="n">move</span><span class="o">(</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="o">,</span> <span class="n">start</span><span class="o">,</span> <span class="n">end</span><span class="o">,</span> <span class="n">sub</span><span class="o">);</span>
<span class="c1">// 서브 타워로 옮겨놨던 원판을 목적지로 옮긴다.</span>
<span class="n">move</span><span class="o">(</span><span class="no">N</span> <span class="o">-</span> <span class="mi">1</span><span class="o">,</span> <span class="n">sub</span><span class="o">,</span> <span class="n">end</span><span class="o">,</span> <span class="n">start</span><span class="o">);</span>
